title: Malaysian Ringgit Hits Highest Since 2018 on AI, Growth Optimism
description: The Malaysian ringgit strengthened to the highest level since 2018, buoyed by optimism over the country’s ties to the artificial intelligence supply chain and the nation’s growth outlook.
